coming requests or perform up to spec.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatDescription</a:Key><a:Value>Does Receive and insert doctor/patient info Process or Doctor info take explicit steps to control resource consumption? Resource consumption attacks can be hard to deal with, and there are times that it makes sense to let the OS do the job.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>StateInformation</a:Key><a:Value>sanitization </a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>InteractionString</a:Key><a:Value>Doctor info</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Priority</a:Key><a:Value>Low</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring></b:Properties><b:SourceGuid>fceece9d-be35-4ded-8001-5f5d8e9a93d5</b:SourceGuid><b:State>Mitigated</b:State><b:StateInformation i:nil="true"/><b:TargetGuid>a8c672b4-71bb-401e-8def-63be97118b15</b:TargetGuid><b:Title i:nil="true"/><b:TypeId>D2</b:TypeId><b:Upgraded>false</b:Upgraded><b:UserThreatCategory i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatDescription i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatShortDescription i:nil="true"/><b:Wide>false</b:Wide></a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:Key>S7.1fceece9d-be35-4ded-8001-5f5d8e9a93d58a7046d3-7d07-4b32-b72c-9b8800c4c6c495ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b</a:Key><a:Value xmlns:b="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/ThreatModeling.KnowledgeBase"><b:ChangedBy>MM-LAP\MM</b:ChangedBy><b:DrawingSurfaceGuid>57c6a81d-ab89-41f7-8386-d21be1669bb2</b:DrawingSurfaceGuid><b:FlowGuid>8a7046d3-7d07-4b32-b72c-9b8800c4c6c4</b:FlowGuid><b:Id>19</b:Id><b:InteractionKey>fceece9d-be35-4ded-8001-5f5d8e9a93d5:8a7046d3-7d07-4b32-b72c-9b8800c4c6c4:95ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b</b:InteractionKey><b:InteractionString i:nil="true"/><b:ModifiedAt>2024-01-11T14:16:33.2802253+03:00</b:ModifiedAt><b:Priority>Low</b:Priority><b:Properties><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Title</a:Key><