attacker to read information not intended for disclosure. </a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>StateInformation</a:Key><a:Value>least privilage principle is applied </a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>InteractionString</a:Key><a:Value>Medical info</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Priority</a:Key><a:Value>Low</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring></b:Properties><b:SourceGuid>23f0fd49-1986-40db-b840-15cc5dff95d7</b:SourceGuid><b:State>Mitigated</b:State><b:StateInformation i:nil="true"/><b:TargetGuid>8a1c5d89-7ebc-4cee-b8df-d8d29dadb9f6</b:TargetGuid><b:Title i:nil="true"/><b:TypeId>I23</b:TypeId><b:Upgraded>false</b:Upgraded><b:UserThreatCategory i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatDescription i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatShortDescription i:nil="true"/><b:Wide>false</b:Wide></a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:Key>R695ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b7647d81d-3102-4dfd-83b2-4f1149d9c4e81722b6fb-3d70-4381-8b62-16ef953092fe</a:Key><a:Value xmlns:b="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/ThreatModeling.KnowledgeBase"><b:ChangedBy>MM-LAP\MM</b:ChangedBy><b:DrawingSurfaceGuid>57c6a81d-ab89-41f7-8386-d21be1669bb2</b:DrawingSurfaceGuid><b:FlowGuid>7647d81d-3102-4dfd-83b2-4f1149d9c4e8</b:FlowGuid><b:Id>31</b:Id><b:InteractionKey>95ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b:7647d81d-3102-4dfd-83b2-4f1149d9c4e8:1722b6fb-3d70-4381-8b62-16ef953092fe</b:InteractionKey><b:InteractionString i:nil="true"/><b:ModifiedAt>2024-01-11T14:20:04.4249988+03:00</b:ModifiedAt><b:Priority>Low</b:Priority><b:Properties><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Title</a:Key><a:Value>Potential Data Repudiation by Retrieve patient info Process</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatCategory</a:Key><a:Value>Repudiation</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatShortDescription</a:Key><a:Value>Repudiation threats involve an adversary denying that something happened.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatDescription</a:Key><a:Value>Retrieve patient info Process claims that it did not receive data from a source outside the trust boundary. </a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>StateInformation</a:Key><a:Value>the Retrieve patient info Process will not be completed if it did not receive the data from Patient info database </a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>InteractionString</a:Key><a:Value>Patient info</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Priority</a:Key><a:Value>Low</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring></b:Properties><b:SourceGuid>95ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b</b:SourceGuid><b:State>NotApplicable</b:State><b:StateInformation i:nil="true"/><b:TargetGuid>1722b6fb-3d70-4381-8b62-16ef953092fe</b:TargetGuid><b:Title i:nil="true"/><b:TypeId>R6</b:TypeId><b:Upgraded>false</b:Upgraded><b:UserThreatCategory i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatDescription i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatShortDescription i:nil="true"/><b:Wide>false</b:Wide></a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:Key>D395ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b7647d81d-3102-4dfd-83b2-4f1149d9c4e81722b6fb-3d70-4381-8b62-16ef953092fe</a:Key><a:Value xmlns:b="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/ThreatModeling.KnowledgeBase"><b:ChangedBy>MM-LAP\MM</b:ChangedBy><b:DrawingSurfaceGuid>57c6a81d-ab89-41f7-8386-d21be1669bb2</b:DrawingSurfaceGuid><b:FlowGuid>7647d81d-3102-4dfd-83b2-4f1149d9c4e8</b:FlowGuid><b:Id>32</b:Id><b:InteractionKey>95ebfb18-d739-47f5-bfca-68768078f89b:7647d81d-3102-4dfd-83b2-4f1149d9c4e8:1722b6fb-3d70-4381-8b62-16ef953092fe</b:InteractionKey><b:InteractionString i:nil="true"/><b:ModifiedAt>2023-12-26T05:04:30.9754154+03:00</b:ModifiedAt><b:Priority>Low</b:Priority><b:Properties><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Title</a:Key><a