ially Interrupted</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatCategory</a:Key><a:Value>Denial Of Service</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatShortDescription</a:Key><a:Value>Denial of Service happens when the process or a datastore is not able to service incoming requests or perform up to spec.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatDescription</a:Key><a:Value>An external agent interrupts data flowing across a trust boundary in either direction.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>StateInformation</a:Key><a:Value>standard mitigation for MITM attacks such as firewalls and DNS configrations are out of scope</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>InteractionString</a:Key><a:Value>Record Keeper info</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Priority</a:Key><a:Value>Low</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring></b:Properties><b:SourceGuid>6cfb4460-4acb-4bc1-90a0-4ae54778b0ca</b:SourceGuid><b:State>NotApplicable</b:State><b:StateInformation i:nil="true"/><b:TargetGuid>2cfff8e7-b780-49f9-93a0-8f71a3b3c5a6</b:TargetGuid><b:Title i:nil="true"/><b:TypeId>D4</b:TypeId><b:Upgraded>false</b:Upgraded><b:UserThreatCategory i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatDescription i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatShortDescription i:nil="true"/><b:Wide>false</b:Wide></a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:Key>D56cfb4460-4acb-4bc1-90a0-4ae54778b0ca3fde2f1e-13a3-41c5-ad3a-7ba9cead59012cfff8e7-b780-49f9-93a0-8f71a3b3c5a6</a:Key><a:Value xmlns:b="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/ThreatModeling.KnowledgeBase"><b:ChangedBy>MM-LAP\MM</b:ChangedBy><b:DrawingSurfaceGuid>57c6a81d-ab89-41f7-8386-d21be1669bb2</b:DrawingSurfaceGuid><b:FlowGuid>3fde2f1e-13a3-41c5-ad3a-7ba9cead5901</b:FlowGuid><b:Id>40</b:Id><b:InteractionKey>6cfb4460-4acb-4bc1-90a0-4ae54778b0ca:3fde2f1e