ory</a:Key><a:Value>Denial Of Service</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatShortDescription</a:Key><a:Value>Denial of Service happens when the process or a datastore is not able to service incoming requests or perform up to spec.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>UserThreatDescription</a:Key><a:Value>An external agent prevents access to a data store on the other side of the trust boundary.</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>StateInformation</a:Key><a:Value>the web server and the database server in the same data center</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>InteractionString</a:Key><a:Value>Medical info</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:KeyValueOfstringstring><a:Key>Priority</a:Key><a:Value>Low</a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringstring></b:Properties><b:SourceGuid>36789562-6c38-4b13-b70f-36c84eb6384a</b:SourceGuid><b:State>NotApplicable</b:State><b:StateInformation i:nil="true"/><b:TargetGuid>23f0fd49-1986-40db-b840-15cc5dff95d7</b:TargetGuid><b:Title i:nil="true"/><b:TypeId>D5</b:TypeId><b:Upgraded>false</b:Upgraded><b:UserThreatCategory i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatDescription i:nil="true"/><b:UserThreatShortDescription i:nil="true"/><b:Wide>false</b:Wide></a:Value></a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:KeyValueOfstringThreatpc_P0_PhOB><a:Key>R6325f951e-256e-4c91-a98d-8cbd302a314f3eeab5fb-13d8-4741-b602-70a1bde68c5e2cfff8e7-b780-49f9-93a0-8f71a3b3c5a6</a:Key><a:Value xmlns:b="http://schemas.datacontract.org/2004/07/ThreatModeling.KnowledgeBase"><b:ChangedBy>MM-LAP\MM</b:ChangedBy><b:DrawingSurfaceGuid>57c6a81d-ab89-41f7-8386-d21be1669bb2</b:DrawingSurfaceGuid><b:FlowGuid>3eeab5fb-13d8-4741-b602-70a1bde68c5e</b:FlowGuid><b:Id>82</b:Id><b:InteractionKey>325f951e-256e-4c91-a98d-8cbd302a314f:3eeab5fb-13d8-4741-b602-70a1bde68c5e:2cfff8e7-b780-49f9-93a0-8f71a3b3c5a6</b:InteractionKey><b:InteractionString i:nil="true"/><b:ModifiedAt>20